<h3 id="深圳湾公园"><a href="#深圳湾公园" class="headerlink" title="深圳湾公园"></a>深圳湾公园</h3><p><img src="https://s.hyli.xyz/gallery/25_HK-GD/IMG_20250818_210559.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="万科云城"><a href="#万科云城" class="headerlink" title="万科云城"></a>万科云城</h3><p><img src="https://s.hyli.xyz/gallery/25_HK-GD/IMG_20250818_205639.jpg"></p>
<h2 id="Day-3-香港"><a href="#Day-3-香港" class="headerlink" title="Day 3: 香港"></a>Day 3: 香港</h2><p>一觉睡到中午，待雨停后才出门。这次选择从深圳湾口岸过关，效率极高，仅用十分钟便顺利通关。过关后乘坐B2路公交到元朗站，再换乘地铁。</p>
<h3 id="元朗"><a href="#元朗" class="headerlink" title="元朗"></a>元朗</h3><p><img src="https://s.hyli.xyz/gallery/25_HK-GD/IMG_20250819_153020.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="中环"><a href="#中环" class="headerlink" title="中环"></a>中环</h3><p><img src="https://s.hyli.xyz/gallery/25_HK-GD/IMG_20250819_185204.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="中环街市"><a href="#中环街市" class="headerlink" title="中环街市"></a>中环街市</h3><p><img src="https://s.hyli.xyz/gallery/25_HK-GD/IMG_20250819_185315.jpg"></p>
